				"description":"<p></p> <p>Our alumni returned to Salim Habib University on May 25, 2025, for a grand Alumni Reunion organized by the Career Placement &amp; Industrial Liaison Office (CPILO).</p> <p></p> <p></p> <p>The highlight of the evening was Qawwali Night, which featured the mesmerizing maestro Qawwal Ashfaq Hussain and group, which enthralled the audience with the melodious music of qawwali. The event also included inspiring yet memorable talks from our esteemed management and engaging and fun activities that brought smiles and laughter to everyone.</p> <p></p> <p></p> <p>It was truly heartwarming to reconnect with our amazing alumni and relive the unforgettable journey we&#8217;ve all shared. We&#8217;re immensely proud of the incredible individuals you&#8217;ve become and wish you good luck in your endeavors!</p> <p></p> <p></p> <p>Until we meet again, SHU family!</p> <p></p> "}</script></div>
