				"description":"<p></p> <p>Salim Habib University was a Support Sponsor at WIBCON RISing 2025, a Women in Business and Leadership Conference organized by the Pakistan Society for Training and Development, which took place in Karachi at the Pearl Continental Hotel on Thursday, May 15, 2025.</p> <p></p> <p></p> <p>The conference, which welcomed 1000+ women from all walks of life, and was attended by representatives from multiple leading corporations, as well as dignitaries, highlighted and celebrated the notable achievements of iconic female leaders, entrepreneurs, and professionals in Pakistan.</p> <p></p> <p></p> <p>Notably present at the event from Salim Habib University were Team Career Placement &amp; Industrial Liaison Office (CPILO), students, and faculty members.</p> <p></p> <p></p> <figure class="wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-2 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex"></p> <figure class='wp-block-image size-large'><img alt="" src='https://shu.edu.pk/wp-content/uploads/whatsapp-image-2025-06-04-at-9.58.03-am-1-768x1024.jpeg.webp' alt='' class='wp-image-30765' /></figure> <p></p> <p></p> <figure class='wp-block-image size-large'><img alt="" src='https://shu.edu.pk/wp-content/uploads/whatsapp-image-2025-06-04-at-2.30.41-pm-edited.jpeg.webp' alt='' class='wp-image-30766' /></figure> <p></p> <p></p> <figure class='wp-block-image size-large'><img alt="" src='https://shu.edu.pk/wp-content/uploads/whatsapp-image-2025-06-04-at-2.30.40-pm-1-768x1024.jpeg.webp' alt='' class='wp-image-30761' /></figure> <p></p> <p></p> <figure class='wp-block-image size-large'><img alt="" src='https://shu.edu.pk/wp-content/uploads/whatsapp-image-2025-06-04-at-2.30.40-pm-768x1024.jpeg.webp' alt='' class='wp-image-30757' /></figure> <p></p> <p></p> <figure class='wp-block-image size-large'><img alt="" src='https://shu.edu.pk/wp-content/uploads/whatsapp-image-2025-06-04-at-2.30.06-pm-edited.jpeg.webp' alt='' class='wp-image-30767' /