				"description":"<p></p> <p>The 1st International Conference on Computing &amp; Artificial Intelligence (ICCA-25), organized by the Faculty of Information Technology, Salim Habib University (SHU), was inaugurated in a grand ceremony at Fatima Business School, SHU, on Thursday, May 15, 2025, in realization of the vision of the University&#8217;s Honourable Chancellor Dr. Iram Afaq and her mission of revolutionizing education in Pakistan through the incorporation of business technology, science, and artificial intelligence.</p> <p></p> <p></p> <p>Chief Guest Mr. Shahzad Shahid, CEO TPS, was warmly welcomed by Conference Patron and Vice Chancellor SHU Prof. Dr. Syed Irfan Hyder, Chief Operating Officer of The Salim Habib Education Foundation Mr. Muhammad Abbas, Registrar Dr. Muhammad Hussain Habib, Dean Faculty of Information Technology Prof. Dr. Sheeraz Arif, and Chairperson Department of Computer Science Dr. Raazia Sosan. Mr. Shahzad Shahid addressed the audience in an inspiring talk during the Inaugural Ceremony, while Prof. Dr. Syed Irfan Hyder delivered the Welcome Address.</p> <p></p> <p></p> <p>The event also featured invigorating keynote sessions by renowned industry experts and academicians, namely Mr. Adnan Zaidi, Chief AI Officer Proxima.pk and Kaggle Grandmaster, Prof. Dr. Muhammad Khurram, Department of Computer and Information Systems Engineering, NED University, Mr. Jibran Jamshad, Education Lead CIS Region and Central Europe &amp; Country Principal Officer Pakistan at Microsoft, and Prof. Dr. Tariq Rahim Soomro, Rector IoBM &amp; Chair, IEEE Karachi Section.</p> <p></p> <p></p> <p>One of the major highlights of the Ceremony was a thought-provoking Panel Discussion on How CEOs Shape Product Strategy with C-suite executives on board, including Mr. Shakeel Akhter, Chief Information Officer Indus Hospital &amp; Health Network, Mr. Shoaib-ur-Rehman, Founder &amp; CEO Virtuosoft Pvt. Ltd., Mr. Mohammad Asif Siddiqui, Founder &amp; CEO OISOL Pvt. Ltd., Mr. Ansab Naqvi, Founder &amp; CEO Asani.io, Mr. Asad Ullah Chaudhry, CEO AUC Technologies, Mr. Mobeen-ul-Haq, CEO Silicon Technologies, Mr. Arbab Ali Khan, Founder &amp; Managing Director Innovarge, and Chief Guest Mr. Shahzad Shahid. The discussion was moderated by Mr. Noor Ali, former Senior Program Manager CISCO, and Prof. Dr. Syed Irfan Hyder.</p> <p></p> <p></p> <p>Day 1 of the conference also featured research paper presentations, poster presentations, project displays, and informative technical sessions, all of which showcased technological and scientific breakthroughs with the potential to reshape the future of Artificial Intelligence, Cybersecurity, Quantum Computing, and other emerging fields.</p> <p></p> <p></p> <p>Notably in attendance were Vice Chancellors of leading Pakistani universities, renowned researchers, esteemed guests from both academia and industry, and Salim Habib University’s Deans, Directors, and Heads, along with Computer Science faculty and students.</p> <p></p> ","organizer":[{"@type":"Organization","name":"Faculty of Information Technology"}]}</script></div>
