				"description":"<p></p> <p>On Friday, May 16, 2025, Salim Habib University organized a rally and a grand flag-hoisting ceremony to observe Youm-e-Tashakur (Day of Gratitude). The day was commemorated to honor the resilience and historic victory of Pakistan military forces during Operation Bunyan-ul-Marsoos, and to pay tribute to the martyrs who sacrificed their lives for the nation.</p> <p></p> <p></p> <p>The University community, including students, faculty, staff, and management actively participated in this rally, displaying a great spirit of patriotism, unity, and leadership.</p> <p></p> <p></p> <p>Mr. Samiuddin Siddiqui, Secretary to the Governor of Sindh, also graced the event with his presence.</p> <p></p> <p></p> <p></p> "}</script></div>
