				"description":"<p></p> <p>Our auditorium echoed with curiosity, admiration, and thoughtful silence as renowned journalist and television anchor <strong>Waseem Badami</strong> graced us with his presence for a special session titled <strong>“Har Lamha Masoomana with Waseem Badami.”</strong></p> <p></p> <p></p> <p class='has-small-font-size'>In a rare and engaging on-campus interview, Badami shared his inspiring journey—from his humble beginnings in Karachi to becoming one of Pakistan’s most respected media personalities. Students listened with rapt attention as he discussed the challenges and responsibilities that come with working in the media industry, emphasizing the importance of integrity, hard work, and emotional intelligence.</p> <p></p> <p></p> <p>The session was marked by witty exchanges, heartfelt moments, and of course, the signature segment <strong>“Masoomana Sawal”</strong> that students eagerly participated in. From media ethics and political neutrality to personal anecdotes and professional advice, Badami candidly responded to a wide range of questions, leaving the audience both enlightened and inspired.</p> <p></p> <p></p> <p>This interactive session wasn’t just about media—it was a learning experience that blended journalism, communication, life values, and leadership in a truly memorable way.</p> <p></p> <p></p> <p>We extend our heartfelt thanks to <strong>Waseem Badami</strong> for his time, sincerity, and unmatched charm, and to all the students and faculty who made this event a grand success.</p> <p></p> <p></p> <p></p> ","organizer":[{"@type":"Organization","name":"Faculty of Information Technology"}]}</script></div>
